      • collectNextHopInterfaces

        public static Map<String,Map<Ip,Set<AbstractRoute>>> collectNextHopInterfaces(GenericRib<AbstractRoute> rib,
                                                                              AbstractRoute route)
        Attempt to resolve a RIB route down to an interface route.
        Parameters:
        rib - GenericRib for which to do the resolution.
        route - AbstractRoute with a next hop IP to be resolved.
        Returns:
        A map (interface name -> last hop IP -> last taken route) for
        Throws:
        BatfishException - if resolution depth is exceeded (high likelihood of a routing loop) OR an invalid route in the RIB has been encountered.
